{"title":"茶","authors":["王华"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":5,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南秀丽的风景里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶，清纯而透明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嵌入贫瘠的土壤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感人的绿色沿山梁延伸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔韧的方式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渗透人们的精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驻足山陵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会听见茶歌清脆不绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嚼一片沾滴茶歌的叶子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种清香沁入心脾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背一背小小的背篓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便能掂出春天的分量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远的茶香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它与炊烟，与雨水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同样渗入我们的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以至于在岁月的沙哑处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓淡之间，一杯茶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总能勾起一段情感……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}